ry or if short introductory content can reasonably be folded into the subsections below them. So the knowledge file's title \"１件ごとの処理\" represents the entire section, with s1 through s8 as its subsections. The excerpt shows s1 and s2 starting with \"エンドレコードの精査処理\" and \"バリデータクラスの終了処理\" at the h3 level, which aligns with them being subsections under the main h2 heading.\n\nThe structural issue is that the intro content for \"１件ごとの処理\" itself appears to be merged into s3 rather than standing as its own introductory subsection. Additionally, there's a missing context reference—\"ファイルバリデータクラスと同様に\"—that should be clarified to understand how this section relates to the broader validation flow. I'm noticing that ExecutionContext shows up consistently across multiple code examples but isn't documented in the hints sections, though it's a standard Nablarch class so this might be acceptable to leave as-is.\n\nLet me verify I haven't missed any other gaps—the cross-references, validation notes, and data tables all appear to be accounted for in the knowledge file, so I think my analysis is complete and ready to structure the findings.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":19970,"cache_read_input_tokens":29807,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":19970,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"99946b74-3967-4b58-a9a5-ad7be38b9313","uuid":"a7149ee5-1e3a-457a-85f4-b6c8f683eba9"}
